Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗 那时也是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克给我这顶帽子的时候 我高兴坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起 快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她们说教之前 我连你的服装都没在意过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我这种男人一起 不辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问清楚 你真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克对我那么温柔 也送我这么漂亮的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我高兴地…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高兴 反而辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丽兹的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是个仿造品 是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克一直后悔给我起名“莉萨”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起时 不管怎样都会想起丽兹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不是丽兹 甚至不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我还是不能和卢克在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我后悔给你起名“莉萨”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我一定出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我后悔的是 让你背负丽兹的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是你 不是丽兹{\fnsimhei}·{\r}奥克伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能走自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别顾虑我 别被丽兹的影子束缚住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过自己想过的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我在一起会妨碍你走自己的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是和卢克一起住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和丽兹没关系 我是出于自己的意志想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经是生息与共的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走完剩下的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这些家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人外会在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认为干脆全部毁灭掉更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙 真动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.20,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur3}锻造师 -Blacksimith-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧吧 烧起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类 城市 一切都烧尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐烂透顶的城市里居住的腐烂透顶的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾就像个垃圾 全变成灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个个都是窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭一次从头再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种美丽的景色可不多见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 我也能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和可靠的骑士在一起 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城 城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来相当不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止人外 还有恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格弗里德那家伙 面子够大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去打倒恶魔和西格弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护这座城市和人民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 对手是恶魔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算在高处悠哉悠哉的旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有笔帐得去跟他算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可得赌上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了生息与共吗 绝不会离开你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让你随心所欲 骑士团的脸不就丢光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气解决它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开沉睡 把握真实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风凝吾手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风啊 贯穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊 野丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但全身湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下 我兜个圈子从那边过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底还有多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别退缩 来一个杀一个来两个杀一双
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美丽 这正是净化腐烂世界的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么认为吗 Blacksmith
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣和你看夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和坎贝尔家的小姑娘一起就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个贴心的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你们一起看夜景的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:10:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们的首级放在这特等席上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很能干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么如此在乎这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种腐烂透顶的城市有多大价值？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位女性对我说 想保护这座城市和这里的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要杀掉你 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怕 从右边绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 卢克不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥塌了 我绕了一圈后卢克就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明约定了永远在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 莉萨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想出卢克去哪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是去和一个叫西格弗里德的男人战斗去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去卢克那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在正和恶魔战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我们就绰绰有余了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去卢克那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号街的瞭望台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我看到塔楼塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想妨碍西格弗里德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨 离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖退下吧 我不想对人类使用魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种微风对我不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是来杀我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和腐蚀之魔剑对刀 真是愚蠢的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使用的透支了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 塞西莉 去卢克那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是休息一下 很快就会追上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约定过吗 两人一起保护城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在你的手中 我才会如此夺目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该决胜负了吧 Blacksmith
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋都快裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专程跑来送死的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是手无寸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那份慈悲心肠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你变成一块块腐肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上莉萨 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不想有人在我面前成为牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹豁出性命保护了心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什么牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别玷污丽兹{\fnsimhei}·{\r}奥克伍德的死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的爱 莉萨的心意 你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要总是藏在鞘中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔出来 摆出架势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和那些玷污她的家伙战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受一切 去战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会成为丽兹最好的宽慰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受…一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉萨 拿出玉钢和刀柄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始锻造
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水挫 小割 选别 积重 锻链
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折返 折返 折返 折返 折返
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 那种身体状况怎么可能锻得出魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}芯铁成形 皮铁成形 造边 素延
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造锋 火造 粗研 覆土 淬火 烧入 锻造研 初研
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备水砥 改正砥 中名仓砥 细名仓砥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内昙地砥 修饰研磨 刀艳地砥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭刀 取刀 打磨 刀帽研磨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收柄！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会犯两次同样的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护你的 塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是独立交易都市 三号街自卫骑士团所属
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手持卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思与莉萨合力打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精雕玉琢之刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为深爱的城市 深爱的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将誓死保卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为尽说这种蠢话 这个世界才会腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们活着就是不可救药的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个个都被瓦尔巴尼尔毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别惹我笑 瓦尔巴尼尔有什么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会用卢克的刀 将瓦尔巴尼尔讨灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管刀有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你这种菜鸟手里 没有一点意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要招式 重要的是有一颗百折不挠的心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫嚣了 小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那把刀 让你的灵魂化作一缕青烟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会忘记你们这几张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔 卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一把不中用的破刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你这把刀 我的心没有折断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我越发相信了卢克的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是最棒的铸刀匠 卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看好你哦 锻造圣剑的Blacksmith
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是个只会锻破刀的Blacksmith
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 城市里还有需要保护的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没打够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 因为我是骑士
